# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This app uses file-based JSON storage by default (data/projects.json).
# No environment variables are required for local development or for running
# on a persistent Node host such as a Hostinger VPS.
#
# If you move the backend to a managed Postgres database (recommended when
# deploying the API on Vercel, whose serverless filesystem is ephemeral), add
# your Neon pooled connection string here and enable the Postgres storage
# driver:
#
# To use Postgres (Neon) instead of the local JSON files:
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@ep-xxxx-pooler.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require"
# STORAGE_DRIVER="postgres"
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
